{"tid":1301544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"議員: 何君堯 \"維特健靈Doctor's Choice醫之選的受薪顧問\"","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:15:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T16:20:38.000Z","uid":235174,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e94420068429d8b6fb37d9bbb0816b9dff86efb4","tid":1301544,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"Legislative Council of Hong Kong document<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/cmi/yr16-20/hky/hky_2.1_20180209_01_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fgeneral%2Fchinese%2Fcmi%2Fyr16-20%2Fhky%2Fhky_2.1_20180209_01_c.pdf&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=079a8f15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/general/chinese/cmi/yr16-20/hky/hky_2.1_20180209_01_c.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFCVEDD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFCVEDD.png&h=3b25cbaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQ6CS0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQ6CS0f.jpg&h=48a7a184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Disclaimer: 以下係一堆無聊剪影, 我對何議員冇任何意見, 我有時都會去新界</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBqL1RZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBqL1RZ.gif&h=a52b51e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QftmAbX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQftmAbX.jpg&h=788ed7cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xojEmR0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxojEmR0.jpg&h=3d019249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://juniusho.blogspot.com/2013/01/blog-post_27.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjuniusho.blogspot.com%2F2013%2F01%2Fblog-post_27.html&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=e03db96f\" target=\"_blank\">http://juniusho.blogspot.com/2013/01/blog-post_27.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/0KYqhnV.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KYqhnV.jpg&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=93cec909\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/0KYqhnV.jpg</a><br />\n維特健靈慈善單車馬拉松<br />\n上周日是一個騎單車的好日子，尤其是沿著海邊的路線。維特健靈在上周日繼去年以來再次舉辦了一個很好的活動。我被安排與莊陳友先生一組進入名人組的比賽。不過，結果並不重要。重要的是過程本身。<br />\n<br />\n真係健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d3221b939b08fc29ac6f6ad7d2338eb1a17fcc3","tid":1301544,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2acaff8bc1cd2eabf6517a7806d93ba670f94e96","tid":1301544,"uid":240347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:17:02.000Z","msg":"6場1號 天祿<br />\n馬主何君堯議員<br />\n<a href=\"https://racing.hkjc.com/racing/Info/meeting/RaceCard/chinese/Local/20190710/HV/6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fracing.hkjc.com%2Fracing%2FInfo%2Fmeeting%2FRaceCard%2Fchinese%2FLocal%2F20190710%2FHV%2F6&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBIE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=1dac3fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://racing.hkjc.com/racing/Info/meeting/RaceCard/chinese/Local/20190710/HV/6</a><br />\n#內幕貼士唔好講人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c283be92374164f92464d5e3ea8de4935a31ee9d","tid":1301544,"uid":235174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:42:24.000Z","msg":"要寫信去質問吓維特健靈點解請黑社會做顧問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse